Pulling method for xpose_set

Source: R/xpose_set.R
pull.xpose_set.Rd

Pulling method for xpose_set

Usage

# S3 method for class 'xpose_set'
pull(.data, ...)

Arguments

.data

<xpose_set> An xpose_set object

...

<dynamic-dots> (passed through to <pull>)

Value

The top-level information for a set requested.

Examples


xpdb_set %>%
  pull(xpdb)
